videos.headline: Tennessee pulls away in 2nd half to advance in the SEC tournament
videos.description: Tennessee gets 20 points from Josiah-Jordan James in a 70-55 win vs. Ole Miss.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Tennessee pulls away in 2nd half to advance in the SEC tournament) 2023/03/09 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Vescovi, James detail Tennessee facing adversity
videos.description: Following the win over Ole Miss, Josiah-Jordan James and Santiago Vescovi describe overcoming obstacles of injuries to achieve victory.

videos.headline: James, Vescovi star as Volunteers cruise past Rebels
videos.description: Josiah-James Jordan (20 points) and Santiago Vescovi (15 points) lead 5-seed Tennessee past 13-seed Ole Miss, 70-55, in the second round of the SEC Tournament.
